{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--prKddKy5GwGL5u_gHBuBU--><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b95f13db504b9bfa.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/9159a2133e09535d.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-66ccd12ae1f5e9ea.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/87c73c54-24122e7b92478d00.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/18-b339bcfc88586b9e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-db96051a16a27532.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><title>Auto Router</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Intelligent LLM routing proxy — automatically picks the best model for every request\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"shell\"><div class=\"landing\"><nav class=\"landing-nav\"><div class=\"landing-nav-brand\"><div class=\"landing-nav-mark\">AR</div><span class=\"landing-nav-name\">Auto Router</span></div><div class=\"landing-nav-links\"><a href=\"#features\">Features</a><a href=\"#how-it-works\">How It Works</a><a href=\"/admin\">Dashboard</a><a href=\"/admin\" class=\"nav-cta\">Get Started</a></div></nav><section class=\"hero\"><div class=\"hero-badge\">OpenAI-Compatible LLM Router</div><h1>Never pick a model again.<br/><span class=\"gradient-text\">Just write prompts.</span></h1><p class=\"hero-sub\">Auto Router reads every prompt and sends it to the right model from your catalog. Claude for code. GPT for chat. Gemini for reasoning. One endpoint, zero if-statements.</p><div class=\"hero-actions\"><a href=\"/admin\" class=\"hero-btn-primary\">Start Routing Free <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#how-it-works\" class=\"hero-btn-secondary\">See How It Works</a></div><div class=\"hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-card\"><div class=\"hero-card-header\"><span class=\"hero-card-label\">Incoming request</span></div><div class=\"hero-card-body\">&quot;Refactor this Python function to use async/await&quot;</div></div><div class=\"hero-arrow\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"hero-card highlight\"><div class=\"hero-card-header\"><span class=\"hero-card-label\">Routed to</span><span class=\"hero-card-badge\">Claude Sonnet 4</span></div><div class=\"hero-card-body small\">Best model for code tasks</div></div></div></section><div class=\"trust-bar\"><div class=\"trust-item\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M16.5 17.5H6.3a.4.4 0 01-.4-.3.4.4 0 01.2-.4l8.6-5.4a1.8 1.8 0 00.7-2.2 1.8 1.8 0 00-1.7-1.2H5.4a.2.2 0 01-.2-.2v-.6c0-.1.1-.2.2-.2h10.1a3.8 3.8 0 013.6 2.5 3.8 3.8 0 01-1.5 4.4l-1 .6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M19.5 14.5a2.5 2.5 0 00-2.5-2.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg>Runs on Cloudflare Workers</div><div class=\"trust-item\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"4 17 10 11 4 5\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"19\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"19\"></line></svg>OpenAI SDK Compatible</div><div class=\"trust-item\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Self-Hosted &amp; Private</div><div class=\"trust-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.01 8.01 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z\"></path></svg>Open Source</div></div><section class=\"landing-section\"><div class=\"section-label\">The Idea</div><h2 class=\"section-heading\">You already know which model is best. Encode it.</h2><p class=\"section-desc\">You know Claude is better for code and GPT is faster for simple tasks. But implementing that logic at runtime — with fallbacks, thread continuity, and cost awareness — is a different problem entirely.</p><div class=\"problem-grid\"><div class=\"problem-card\"><div class=\"problem-icon red\">✕</div><h3>Routing logic in app code</h3><p>Model-selection ternaries scattered across your codebase. Every new model means another branch, another deploy.</p></div><div class=\"problem-card\"><div class=\"problem-icon amber\">⚠</div><h3>No fallback on failure</h3><p>A provider goes down and your users get 500s. You hardcoded one model — there’s no plan B unless you build one.</p></div><div class=\"problem-card\"><div class=\"problem-icon orange\">↑</div><h3>Context lost between turns</h3><p>Even if you route well on the first message, continuations land on a different model. KV caches are wasted and conversations break.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"landing-section\" id=\"how-it-works\"><div class=\"section-label\">How It Works</div><h2 class=\"section-heading\">One line in your code. All the smarts in ours.</h2><p class=\"section-desc\">Tell us which models you trust and when to use them. We handle the rest: reading prompts, picking models, failing over, and keeping conversations on track.</p><div class=\"flow-container\"><div class=\"flow-step\"><div class=\"flow-marker\"><div class=\"flow-number\">01</div><div class=\"flow-line\"></div></div><div class=\"flow-content\"><h3>Pick your models</h3><p>Add the models you want to use. Claude for code, GPT for quick chat, Gemini for long context—whatever fits your needs.</p><div class=\"flow-pills\"><span class=\"flow-pill\">Claude Sonnet 4</span><span class=\"flow-pill\">GPT-4.1 Mini</span><span class=\"flow-pill\">o3</span><span class=\"flow-pill\">Gemini 2.5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flow-step\"><div class=\"flow-marker\"><div class=\"flow-number\">02</div><div class=\"flow-line\"></div></div><div class=\"flow-content\"><h3>Tell us the rules—in plain English</h3><p>No JSON. No code. Just describe when to use each model. &quot;Use Claude for anything with code.&quot; &quot;Use the cheapest model for simple questions.&quot;</p><div class=\"flow-quote\">“Prefer Claude for code. Use GPT-4.1-mini for chat. Pick thinking models for math.”</div></div></div><div class=\"flow-step\"><div class=\"flow-marker\"><div class=\"flow-number\">03</div><div class=\"flow-line\"></div></div><div class=\"flow-content\"><h3>Send prompts. Get answers.</h3><p>Use <code class=\"code\">model: &quot;auto&quot;</code> in your OpenAI SDK. We read each prompt, route it to the right model, and handle failures automatically.</p><div class=\"flow-code simple\"><span style=\"color:var(--indigo)\">await</span> openai.chat.completions.create(<!-- -->{<!-- -->\n<!-- -->  <!-- -->model: <span style=\"color:var(--green)\">&quot;auto&quot;</span>,<!-- -->\n<!-- -->  <!-- -->messages<!-- -->\n<!-- -->}<!-- -->)</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"landing-section\" id=\"features\"><div class=\"section-label centered\">What You Get</div><h2 class=\"section-heading centered\">Smart routing. Zero headaches.</h2><p class=\"section-desc centered\">Everything you need to stop worrying about model selection— so you can focus on building.</p><div class=\"features-grid\"><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot cyan\"></div><h3>Right Model, Every Time</h3></div><p>Our classifier reads your prompts and routes them to the best model from your catalog. Code goes to Claude, summaries to GPT.</p></div><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot indigo\"></div><h3>Plain English Rules</h3></div><p>Just tell us &quot;Use Claude for code&quot; or &quot;Pick the cheapest model for simple questions.&quot; No JSON, no code, no redeploys.</p></div><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot green\"></div><h3>Conversations Stay Coherent</h3></div><p>Once a model handles a thread, it stays pinned. Multi-turn chats don&#x27;t switch models mid-conversation. Context is preserved.</p></div><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot amber\"></div><h3>Profiles for Different Needs</h3></div><p>Create <code class=\"code\">auto-cheap</code> for internal tools, <code class=\"code\">auto-coding</code> for your IDE, and <code class=\"code\">auto-fast</code> for customer support.</p></div><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot cyan\"></div><h3>Automatic Failover</h3></div><p>If a provider is down or slow, we automatically try the next best model. Your users never see a 500.</p></div><div class=\"feature-cell\"><div class=\"feature-icon-row\"><div class=\"feature-dot indigo\"></div><h3>See Every Decision</h3></div><p>Query any request ID to see exactly why a model was chosen, what the confidence was, and what the fallback chain looked like.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"landing-section\"><div class=\"section-label\">Configuration</div><h2 class=\"section-heading\">Change models without changing code.</h2><p class=\"section-desc\">Add a new model, update your rules, or create a new profile—all from the dashboard. Your code never changes. It just keeps sending <code class=\"code\">model: &quot;auto&quot;</code>.</p><div class=\"compare\"><div class=\"compare-pane\"><div class=\"compare-header before\">Without Auto Router</div><div class=\"compare-body plain\"><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-x\">✘</span><span>Write if-statements for every model decision</span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-x\">✘</span><span>Handle failures and retries yourself</span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-x\">✘</span><span>Redeploy to add a new model</span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-x\">✘</span><span>Context lost when switching models mid-chat</span></div></div></div><div class=\"compare-pane\"><div class=\"compare-header after\">With Auto Router</div><div class=\"compare-body plain\"><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-check\">✔</span><span>One line: <code>model: &quot;auto&quot;</code></span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-check\">✔</span><span>Automatic failover when models fail</span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-check\">✔</span><span>Update models in the dashboard instantly</span></div><div class=\"compare-item\"><span class=\"compare-check\">✔</span><span>Conversations stay on one model</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"landing-section\"><div class=\"section-label\">Routing Profiles</div><h2 class=\"section-heading\">One router, many strategies.</h2><p class=\"section-desc\">Create named profiles that act as virtual model names. Each profile can override the model catalog, routing instructions, and defaults — so different parts of your app get different routing behavior from the same endpoint.</p><div class=\"profiles-row\"><div class=\"profile-preview\"><div class=\"profile-preview-id\">auto-cheap</div><p class=\"profile-preview-desc\">Restrict the catalog to low-cost models. Great for internal tools, batch jobs, and simple chat.</p><span class=\"profile-tag cyan\">filtered catalog</span><span class=\"profile-tag indigo\">cost-first rules</span></div><div class=\"profile-preview\"><div class=\"profile-preview-id\">auto-coding</div><p class=\"profile-preview-desc\">Only high-thinking models. Custom instructions that prefer Claude for code and o3 for algorithms.</p><span class=\"profile-tag cyan\">thinking models only</span><span class=\"profile-tag indigo\">code-first rules</span></div><div class=\"profile-preview\"><div class=\"profile-preview-id\">auto-support</div><p class=\"profile-preview-desc\">Customer-facing tier. Fast models with guardrails. Blocklist anything experimental.</p><span class=\"profile-tag cyan\">fast defaults</span><span class=\"profile-tag indigo\">strict blocklist</span></div></div></section><section class=\"bottom-cta\"><h2>Define your routing strategy in minutes.</h2><p>Open source. Self-hosted on Cloudflare. Add your models, write your rules, and start routing.</p><div class=\"bottom-cta-actions\"><a href=\"/admin\" class=\"hero-btn-primary\">Open Dashboard <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#how-it-works\" class=\"hero-btn-secondary\">Read the Docs</a></div></section><footer class=\"landing-footer\"><div class=\"landing-footer-left\">Auto Router — open-source LLM routing proxy</div><div class=\"landing-footer-right\"><a href=\"/admin\">Dashboard</a><a href=\"#how-it-works\">Docs</a><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></div></footer></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-66ccd12ae1f5e9ea.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[5341,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[25,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n11:I[4431,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/b95f13db504b9bfa.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/9159a2133e09535d.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"prKddKy5GwGL5u_gHBuBU\\\",\\\"p\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\"],\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],[\\\"\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/css/b95f13db504b9bfa.css\\\",\\\"precedence\\\":\\\"next\\\",\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"nonce\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\"}]],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"html\\\",null,{\\\"lang\\\":\\\"en\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"head\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",null,{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"preconnect\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",null,{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"preconnect\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\\\",\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"anonymous\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+S