assName\":\"problem-icon orange\",\"children\":\"↑\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Context lost between turns\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Even if you route well on the first message, continuations land on a different model. KV caches are wasted and conversations break.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n8:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"landing-section\",\"id\":\"how-it-works\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-label\",\"children\":\"How It Works\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":\"One line in your code. All the smarts in ours.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"section-desc\",\"children\":\"Tell us which models you trust and when to use them. We handle the rest: reading prompts, picking models, failing over, and keeping conversations on track.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-step\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-marker\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-number\",\"children\":\"01\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-line\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Pick your models\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Add the models you want to use. Claude for code, GPT for quick chat, Gemini for long context—whatever fits your needs.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-pills\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-pill\",\"children\":\"Claude Sonnet 4\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-pill\",\"children\":\"GPT-4.1 Mini\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-pill\",\"children\":\"o3\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-pill\",\"children\":\"Gemini 2.5\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-step\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-marker\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-number\",\"children\":\"02\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-line\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Tell us the rules—in plain English\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"No JSON. No code. Just describe when to use each model. \\\"Use Claude for anything with code.\\\" \\\"Use the cheapest model for simple questions.\\\"\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-quote\",\"children\":\"“Prefer Claude for code. Use GPT-4.1-mini for chat. Pick thinking models for math.”\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-step\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-marker\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-number\",\"children\":\"03\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-line\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Send prompts. Get answers.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Use \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"className\":\"code\",\"children\":\"model: \\\"auto\\\"\"}],\" in your OpenAI SDK. We read each prompt, route it to the right model, and handle failures automatically.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-code simple\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"var(--indigo)\"},\"children\":\"await\"}],\" openai.chat.completions.create(\",\"{\",\"\\n\",\"  \",\"model: \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"var(--green)\"},\"children\":\"\\\"auto\\\"\"}],\",\",\"\\n\",\"  \",\"messages\",\"\\n\",\"}\",\")\"]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"landing-section\",\"id\":\"features\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-label centered\",\"children\":\"What You Get\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading centered\",\"children\":\"Smart routing. Zero headaches.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"section-desc centered\",\"children\":\"Everything you need to stop worrying abo